<p>The crying, anger, and mood swings are far worse than anything I experienced prior to being on the drug. I found this website because I was wondering if what I was going through was common or normal. But hey on the bright side I had my first erection in over 10 years! Hanging on in Oregon. Reply Link Susan July 3, ,  Also, hang in there.</p>
<p>I'v had a headache for 3 days now, very teary and basically feel crap having just stopped them. I can't understand why my doctor just stopped them straight away.</p>
